llm_outputs.rationale: The table shows different minimum lot sizes for the B-2 (Marine Business District) zone, depending on the availability of public water and sewer. The values are 20,000 sq ft with no public water or sewer, 15,000 sq ft with either public water or sewer, and 10,000 sq ft with both public water and sewer.
llm_outputs.answer: 20,000 sq ft (no public water/sewer); 15,000 sq ft (public water or sewer); 10,000 sq ft (public water and sewer)
